Request for Proposal: Software Development Services

Project Overview:
We are seeking a qualified software development partner to create a comprehensive web application...

sections.title: Project Overview
sections.content: This RFP seeks proposals for developing a customer management system with advanced reporting capabilities.

sections.title: Technical Requirements
sections.content: System must support 1000+ concurrent users, integrate with existing CRM, provide real-time analytics.

sections.title: Budget and Timeline
sections.content: Project budget: $75,000 - $125,000. Timeline: 8 months from contract execution.
